## Setup & Run

### Requirements
- Arduino IDE + ESP32 board support
- Two ESP32 DevKit boards
- USB cable and power source

### Steps
1. Open `firmware/receiver/receiver.ino`
2. Set `senderMAC` to the sender MAC from Serial Monitor
3. Flash to first ESP32
4. Power receiver with a power bank / charger
5. Open `firmware/sender/sender.ino`
6. Set `receiverMAC` to the receiver MAC
7. Flash to second ESP32
8. Open Serial Monitor on sender at 115200
